{
  "stem": "21139.4",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "How were you wearing your hair in those days?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I had it longer.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But then it was cut shorter because of the-- you know, the lice [INAUDIBLE] to get rid of it and all this.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But only later on, when I was in-- when I was liberated-- or when I was free-- let's say when I was working in-- with people in France-- I let it grow a little bit longer because I didn't have the money to have my hair cut.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I left it long.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I pulled it up so it should look neat.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were also-- Margot was very good in sewing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So the-- the director of the home, she gave her things to sew for herself.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- and Amelie, she didn't do too much.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She helped wherever she was asked to help.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Vic-sur-Cere, I was until February 1944.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I was there from December '42 to February '44.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There, we received the false papers [INAUDIBLE] with our names.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Our names were changed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Mine was Elise [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And because we had to travel-- and the Germans were coming, so we had to leave.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The-- the-- the home was liquidated.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And everybody was sent to different places.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Amelie-- as I said before, Emily and-- and Margot, they went to work for people in Saint-Jean-en-Royans, it was called-- a small place.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they got a family through the people where they worked for me to go there to work to take care of their children, and the cleaning, and-- and so on.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And that home, or the OSE, I suppose, gave them the money to-- for me to travel.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And this is when we got the papers.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The director of that home took care of it.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
